videos.description: Notre Dame tallies 8 unanswered points in the 1st quarter engineered by the stellar passing of Arike Ogunbowale.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale dimes up Young, Turner on Notre Dame 8-0 run

videos.description: Louisville's Asia Durr jumps the passing lane and picks off Marina Mabrey, then taking it coast-to-coast for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Louisville's Durr drops 16 points early vs. No. 1 Notre Dame

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale cuts Asia Durr off on the break and steals the ball, setting up a lofted pass inside to Brianna Turner for a Notre Dame layup.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale picks Durr clean, lobs oop to Turner

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale's foot hovers over Arica Carter's face after a shooting foul, triggering Carter to flair her feet in a scrap below the rim.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale, Carter get chippy after hard foul in paint

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale gives Notre Dame a double-digit lead entering the final frame as she splashes a straight-away 3 to end the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale buries 3 to beat buzzer

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale tees up a 3-pointer from the right wing to put Notre Dame up by seven points with less than a minute to go.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale buries cold-blooded dagger 3

videos.description: Louisville records its first loss of the season as Arike Ogunbowale's 30-point night edges Asia Durr's 29 in Notre Dame's 82-68 home win.
